 160h-64v-84c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v84zm64-172c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40zm0-96c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40zm0-96c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12V76c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40z\"></path></svg>Provincia *</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition\" placeholder=\"Ingresa provincia\" name=\"provincia\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-1\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" class=\"text-gray-500\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M436 480h-20V24c0-13.255-10.745-24-24-24H56C42.745 0 32 10.745 32 24v456H12c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12v20h448v-20c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12zM128 76c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12V76zm0 96c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40zm52 148h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12zm76 160h-64v-84c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v84zm64-172c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40zm0-96c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-40c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40zm0-96c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-40c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12V76c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h40c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v40z\"></path></svg>Distrito *</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition\" placeholder=\"Ingresa distrito\" name=\"distrito\"/></div></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b-2 border-primary-600 pb-3 flex items-center gap-3\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" class=\"text-primary-600 text-2xl\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M621.16 54.46C582.37 38.19 543.55 32 504.75 32c-123.17-.01-246.33 62.34-369.5 62.34-30.89 0-61.76-3.92-92.65-13.72-3.47-1.1-6.95-1.62-10.35-1.62C15.04 79 0 92.32 0 110.81v317.26c0 12.63 7.23 24.6 18.84 29.46C57.63 473.81 96.45 480 135.25 480c123.17 0 246.34-62.35 369.51-62.35 30.89 0 61.76 3.92 92.65 13.72 3.47 1.1 6.95 1.62 10.35 1.62 17.21 0 32.25-13.32 32.25-31.81V83.93c-.01-12.64-7.24-24.6-18.85-29.47zM48 132.22c20.12 5.04 41.12 7.57 62.72 8.93C104.84 170.54 79 192.69 48 192.69v-60.47zm0 285v-47.78c34.37 0 62.18 27.27 63.71 61.4-22.53-1.81-43.59-6.31-63.71-13.62zM320 352c-44.19 0-80-42.99-80-96 0-53.02 35.82-96 80-96s80 42.98 80 96c0 53.03-35.83 96-80 96zm272 27.78c-17.52-4.39-35.71-6.85-54.32-8.44 5.87-26.08 27.5-45.88 54.32-49.28v57.72zm0-236.11c-30.89-3.91-54.86-29.7-55.81-61.55 19.54 2.17 38.09 6.23 55.81 12.66v48.89z\"></path></svg>Identificación del Bien Contratado</h3><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Bien o Servicio *</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition\" placeholder=\"Ej: Aire acondicionado, Servicio técnico, etc.\" name=\"bien_servicio\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Monto reclamado (S/) *</label><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"absolute left-3 top-3 text-gray-500 font-bold\">S/</span><input type=\"number\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"0\" class=\"w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition\" placeholder=\"0.00\" name=\"monto_reclamado\"/></div></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Descripción del bien o servicio *</label><textarea name=\"descripcion_bien\" rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition resize-none\" placeholder=\"Describa el bien o servicio adquirido...\"></textarea></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 border-b-2 border-primary-600 pb-3 flex items-center gap-3\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" class=\"text-primary-600 text-2xl\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M336 64h-80c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64s-64 28.7-64 64H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v352c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h288c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V112c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM96 424c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24 24 10.7 24 24-10.7 24-24 24zm0-96c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24 24 10.7 24 24-10.7 24-24 24zm0-96c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24 24 10.7 24 24-10.7 24-24 24zm96-192c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24-24-10.7-24-24 10.7-24 24-24zm128 368c0 4.4-3.6 8-8 8H168c-4.4 0-8-3.6-8-8v-16c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8h144c4.4 0 8 3.6 8 8v16zm0-96c0 4.4-3.6 8-8 8H168c-4.4 0-8-3.6-8-8v-16c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8h144c4.4 0 8 3.6 8 8v16zm0-96c0 4.4-3.6 8-8 8H168c-4.4 0-8-3.6-8-8v-16c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8h144c4.4 0 8 3.6 8 8v16z\"></path></svg>Detalle de su reclamo</h3><div class=\"bg-primary-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4\"><p class=\"text-sm text-primary-800 mb-2 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 8C119.043 8 8 119.083 8 256c0 136.997 111.043 248 248 248s248-111.003 248-248C504 119.083 392.957 8 256 8zm0 110c23.196 0 42 18.804 42 42s-18.804 42-42 42-42-18.804-42-42 18.804-42 42-42zm56 254c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12h-88c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-24c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h12v-64h-12c-6.627 0-12-5.373-12-12v-24c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12h64c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v100h12c6.627 0 12 5.373 12 12v24z\"></path></svg>Definiciones según el Código del Consumidor:</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm\"><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border border-primary-200\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-red-600\">Reclamo:</p><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Disconformidad con bienes adquiridos o servicios prestados.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border border-primary-200\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-red-600\">Queja:</p><p class=\"text-gray-700\">Malestar por atención, trato u otros aspectos no relacionados al giro.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Tipo *</label><select name=\"tipo_reclamo\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition bg-white\"><option value=\"\">Seleccione tipo</option><option value=\"reclamo\">Reclamo</option><option value=\"queja\">Queja</option></select></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Fecha del hecho reclamado *</label><input type=\"date\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition\" name=\"fecha_hecho\"/></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Descripción detallada *</label><textarea name=\"descripcion\" rows=\"6\" maxLength=\"1000\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition resize-none\" placeholder=\"Describa detalladamente los hechos...\"></textarea><div class=\"flex justify-between mt-2\"><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Incluya todos los detalles relevantes.</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">0<!-- -->/1000 caracteres</p></div></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Pedido o solución esperada *</label><textarea name=\"pedido\" rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 transition resize-none\" placeholder=\"Especifique claramente qué solución espera recibir...\"></textarea></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-6 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary-200\"><div><label for=\"declaracion\" class=\"text-gray-900 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" class=\"text-primary-600\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M466.5 83.7l-192-80a48.15 48.15 0 0 0-36.9 0l-192 80C27.7 91.1 16 108.6 16 128c0 198.5 114.5 335.7 221.5 380.3 11.8 4.9 25.1 4.9 36.9 0C360.1 472.6 496 349.3 496 128c0-19.4-11.7-36.9-29.5-44.3zM256.1 446.3l-.1-381 175.9 73.3c-3.3 151.4-82.1 261.1-175.8 307.7z\"></path></svg>DECLARACIÓN Y CONSENTIMIENTO *</label><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\"><strong>Declaro que los datos consignados son correctos y fiel expresión de la verdad.</strong> <!-- -->Los datos personales serán tratados conforme a la Ley de Protección de Datos Personales (Ley N° 29733).</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"flex-1 py-4 px-6 font-bold rounded-xl transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-lg \n                      bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M476 3.2L12.5 270.6c-18.1 10.4-15.8 35.6 2.2 43.2L121 358.4l287.3-253.2c5.5-4.9 13.3 2.6 8.6 8.3L176 407v80.5c0 23.6 28.5 32.9 42.5 15.8L282 426l124.6 52.2c14.2 6 30.4-2.9 33-18.2l72-432C515 7.8 493.3-6.8 476 3.2z\"></path></svg>Enviar Reclamo</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex-1 py-4 px-6 font-bold bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition shadow hover:shadow-lg\">Limpiar Formulario</button></div></form></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-1\"><div class=\"sticky top-24 space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 640 512\" class=\"text-primary-600\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 336h-.02c0-16.18 1.34-8.73-85.05-181.51-17.65-35.29-68.19-35.36-85.87 0C-2.06 328.75.02 320.33.02 336H0c0 44.18 57.31 80 128 80s128-35.82 128-80zM128 176l72 144H56l72-144zm511.98 160c0-16.18 1.34-8.73-85.05-181.51-17.65-35.29-68.19-35.36-85.87 0-87.12 174.26-85.04 165.84-85.04 181.51H384c0 44.18 57.31 80 128 80s128-35.82 128-80h-.02zM440 320l72-144 72 144H440zm88 128H352V153.25c23.51-10.29 41.16-31.48 46.39-57.25H528c8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16V48c0-8.84-7.16-16-16-16H383.64C369.04 12.68 346.09 0 320 0s-49.04 12.68-63.64 32H112c-8.84 0-16 7.16-16 16v32c0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16h129.61c5.23 25.76 22.87 46.96 46.39 57.25V448H112c-8.84 0-16 7.16-16 16v32c0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16h416c8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16v-32c0-8.84-7.16-16-16-16z\"></path></svg>Tus derechos</h3><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" class=\"text-green-600\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/